---
Additional details: The place is filthy every apartment has bed bugs. You pay to spray not the owner. Not hot water, they were forced to get new tanks by hud but they don't have them on. They kept one old tank and  that produces luke warm water that's it. No activities except smoking meth, pot an cigarettes. No one bothers to go outside not even the air head secretary. She lies fluently don't ever believe her for minute. Not maitenance is done unless you pay for it. 20 dollars to get a bulb changed in your apartment. This is an awful bad place to live.$review$,         -- comment
